"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ivf1703097522105.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ivf1703097522105.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ivf1703097522105.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xww1665702658183\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Gold and Super Key Combinations\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Gold and Super key combinations are defined with <code class=\"ph codeph\">^GOLD_BASE_SET</code>. By default, these key combinations are available in all keyboard translation tables in the USYS library that support a Gold key.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ecs1703254253418.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecs1703254253418.html\" title=\"A complete set of keystroke combinations is available in all the keyboard translation tables supplied in the USYS library. These keystroke combinations are defined by the macro ^GOLD_BASE_SET and are the same for every keyboard, unless they are not defined in the keyboard translation table being used. These, or default mappings of your own, should be included in any keyboard translation table you create.\">Default Key Combinations</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xww1665702658183__section_xjv_nbv_yzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d592084e67\"> Gold key </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xww1665702658183__p_d64451e1_d64452e1_d64453e1\">When used within a field, many Gold key combinations are\n        recognized only in unifields and not as another type of widget. This is indicated in the\n        column Unifield only?.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xww1665702658183__p_d64454e1_d64455e1_d64456e1\">To locate keys GOLD, INSERT, REMOVE, and DETAIL, see the\n        keyboard layout for your keyboard.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Function key combinations for all keyboards</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> Keystrokes </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"> Structure editor function </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"> Unifield only? </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"4\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1 xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2 xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3 xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Subfield separator: </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD ; </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Subfield separator. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"4\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1 xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2 xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3 xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Profile characters : </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Match 0-<var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> characters. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD ? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Match any single character. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD = </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Is equal to. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD &gt; </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Is greater than. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD &lt; </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Is less than. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD ! </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Logical NOT. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD &amp; </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__4\"> Logical AND. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__1\"> GOLD | </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xww1665702658183__table_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1__entry__2\"></